attributes.name: KATAME
attributes.description: Hola, somos un pequeño grupo que se dedicará a traer traducciones de algún manga que nos guste o se nos pida, si quieren proponer algún manga o quieren unirse pueden ingresar a nuestro servidor de Discord, ahí les podremos ayudar.

attributes.name: Muslos no Sekai
attributes.description:
¡Estamos reclutando! 
Si sabes algún otro idioma además del español o si eres diestro en el Photoshop y quieres contribuir con este noble scan, no dudes en ayudarnos! 

Necesitamos: Traductores, Cleaners, Redrawers, Typesetters, Coloristas. 

Si estás interesado puedes mandar un mensaje a nuestras redes: 

[Facebook](https://www.facebook.com/MuslosnoSekai)
[Patreon](https://www.patreon.com/MuslosNoSeka)

¡¡Te estaremos esperando!!

attributes.name: Immortal Updates Scan
attributes.description:
We are Immortal updates scan. We translates Chinese Manhua and Korean Manhwa with the help of our team. To get more info and to contact us, visit our discord. Last thing, We are the Group of people who loves reading Manhua and Manhwa.  
  
Visit our site for early Releases! : immortalupdates.com  
Support us on Patreon: [patreon.com/immortal\_updates](http://patreon.com/immortal_updates)  
Contact: immortalupdates@gmail.com

attributes.name: Black Kodou
attributes.description: Black Kodou is a scanlation group that has picked up the manga "Yami no Kodou" after Bamboo Feathers has dropped the project.

attributes.name: SquigglesJP
attributes.description:
The SquigglesJP group is a relaxed, cute girls and bois loving scanalation team, run by Queen SquigglesJP!  
  
We pride ourselves on always striving to improve, rather than expecting each member's work to be the absolute perfection!  
We are currently searching for Japanese to English translators, who feels comfortable enough to translate a manga, even if they're still learning, or make mistakes!  
  
Feel free to hang out on the discord, or even apply for a position!  
<https://discord.gg/uYTqhE8>

If you're able to support us, visit <https://ko-fi.com/squigglesjp>

attributes.name: Timeless scans
attributes.description:
Timeless Scans started in August 2015 as a two-man group. Currently, we are a really close, and chatty, team of over 30 people, and growing. We love to talk to our readers, so you can always hit us up on our public Discord and chat with us, which is over 1000 people and counting. There is almost always a team member available and online in our public discord so if you have any questions about any of our releases, or just general questions, you can get an answer pretty much right away. You can also suggest future projects you’d like to see us take on. We are a nice, close-knit group, with five friendly mods who are available to ensure that the chat is always welcoming and friendly, so don’t be shy and come on by!  
  
We hope to see you soon in our Discord and as always we hope you'll keep supporting and reading our future releases!  
  
If you want to help out or donate it can be done through our site. Have a nice day!
